<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>农行网上支付平台-商户接口范例-支付请求</TITLE>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no" />
